{"tid":1939560,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個仆街做文宣屈人殺人犯","createTime":"2020-03-23T08:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T10:08:50.000Z","uid":257890,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9668adcd01c624079f55d069603e7f0fb646a420","tid":1939560,"uid":257890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T08:18:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/moSjDMt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmoSjDMt.png&h=538fd67f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事源1月9號 呢個ac聲稱有個admin跳樓自殺死咗 當時仼何證據都冇 但個個都因為個文宣ac係多人fol覺得有保證而信哂 而被屈殺人犯嘅女仔嘅個人資料公諸於世咗 比人電話騷擾 喺連登ig比人追擊 出街驚比手足私了 喺屋企驚狗上門拉 被冠名殺人犯嘅女仔呢兩個月提心吊膽 而佢只係得中四<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果？兩個月後今日 fight for 5 demands出黎低調開po講句sorry囉當乜事都冇發生過<br />\n而家啲文宣咁撚樣嫁咩？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f6KxYOn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff6KxYOn.png&h=7ffb393e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最新呢個po 有把女聲彈出黎唔知講乜尻 似乎係企圖撇清關係 定又係精神分裂 自編自導自演？<br />\n我唔撚理佢成個ac有幾多人 總之佢再唔做實質野去同個「殺人犯」女仔賠罪 我有野再爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b2db581e42e6e22ea03bad1455846c1be6cdf4f","tid":1939560,"uid":257890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T08:19:28.000Z","msg":"p牌冇得推 麻煩手足幫幫手 一撚定唔可以比呢啲禍害人間嘅文宣繼續營運"},{"pid":"121604d8a647879fd53d19796662c9cba71aa567","tid":1939560,"uid":257890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T08:19:39.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"49cb8c9737c9755479fb17b103a0d65e89f263f1","tid":1939560,"uid":257890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T08:19:49.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"e3b046ee0d645b4bd0d28f88d9ae2fb1de7b1cd9","tid":1939560,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49cb8c9737c9755479fb17b103a0d65e89f263f1","tid":1939560,"uid":257890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"repl